-align: -0.338ex; width:1.678ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \Om=
ega }"></span>. The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Power_set" tit=
le=3D"Power set">power set</a> of the sample space is formed by considering=
